Title: fix escaping in path parameters
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Component: rest-api
Date: 1653420515
Edition: cre
Knowledge: doc
Level: 1
Version: 2.2.0i1

Previously the REST API sent links containing characters (e.g. ':') which were not properly escaped.
Using them directly without additional escaping could result in a HTTP 404 error.

This is now fixed. No further action is neccessary.
